{"tid":2406033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文: 祝福黃秋生, 杜汶澤等香港朋友","createTime":"2021-02-13T01:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T08:37:32.000Z","uid":134071,"like":567,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"01588b6e5e43f955796398b0a7fbe13bfd8061c8","tid":2406033,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T01:12:02.000Z","msg":"現時正身在台灣的黃秋生，雖然人在異鄉，但他也不愁寂寞，年三十晚與黃明志及幾位朋友一齊食年夜飯。原來除了黃明志外，秋生早前亦與同在台灣的杜汶澤及身兼台灣樂隊「閃靈」主音及現任立法委員的林昶佐（Freddy）等一齊食飯，而台灣總統蔡英文睇相後更親自留言祝福香港人平安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210212/2FXZCNJYW5B57PFAZAJ4TKXHYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210212%2F2FXZCNJYW5B57PFAZAJ4TKXHYE%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=6a01ae07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210212%2F2FXZCNJYW5B57PFAZAJ4TKXHYE%2F&h=c23746dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210212/2FXZCNJYW5B57PFAZAJ4TKXHYE/</a>"},{"pid":"36757e99fc9c058bdce1ddd634726808c860f8ab","tid":2406033,"uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T01:12:35.000Z","msg":"蔡英文原留言<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/limfreddy/posts/1573666399511252?comment_id=1579715868906305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flimfreddy%2Fposts%2F1573666399511252%3Fcomment_id%3D1579715868906305&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=79d14c9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/limfreddy/posts/1573666399511252?comment_id=1579715868906305</a>"},{"pid":"16cc6f5dceac996ed439503553639b364e2cecc9","tid":2406033,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T01:14:21.000Z","msg":"祝好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9933e5286bfab6de7ea83a054d74ca6564386d33","tid":2406033,"uid":134071,"lik